WEBVTT

00:09:59.007 --> 00:10:01.259
that's sort of our aspirational self.

00:10:02.133 --> 00:10:04.482
And it works out much better
to please people

00:10:04.506 --> 00:10:06.958
to look at the actual choices
that they make,

00:10:06.982 --> 00:10:11.745
their revealed preferences
by how much they enjoy simple pleasures.

00:10:12.493 --> 00:10:15.267
